  <brief_title>Efficacy of Combined Oral L-Ornithine-L-Aspartate and Lactulose in Patients With Hepatic Encephalopathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Combined Oral L-Ornithine-L-Aspartate and Oral Lactulose in Patients With Hepatic Encephalopathy</official_title>
